About a week ago, finally solved problem with State Disability and am now getting full payments. 

Going to the doctor on the 5th, and will see if there is a date he will release me to go back the work. Libery Mutual has set a date of 7/17, but my regular doctor did not like that date, but has deferred the decision to my orthopedic doctor, who I will see in a couple of days.
